WEBVTT

00:00:00.930 --> 00:00:03.830
We'd always been kept safe.

00:00:04.650 --> 00:00:08.020
By a teacher as overprotective as he was tough—

00:00:08.570 --> 00:00:12.860
a teacher who had learned life's lessons ahead of us.

00:00:15.990 --> 00:00:16.030


00:00:15.990 --> 00:00:19.990
24th Period Akabane Karma Graduation Time

00:00:21.560 --> 00:00:24.170
