00:00:52.540 --> 00:00:54.700
Is that so, Korosensei?

00:01:00.800 --> 00:01:04.080
Phew... I'm beat.

00:01:04.930 --> 00:01:09.050
Having collapsed, Korosensei seemed unusually satisfied...

00:01:10.020 --> 00:01:12.870
and unusually frail.

00:01:13.970 --> 00:01:15.220
Class?

00:01:16.110 --> 00:01:20.220
What kind of an assassin would let a dying target escape?

00:01:22.480 --> 00:01:24.140
Don't you see?

00:01:24.770 --> 00:01:26.520
It's killing time.

00:01:29.410 --> 00:01:31.360
All good things...

00:01:32.450 --> 00:01:34.820
must come to an end.

00:01:35.700 --> 00:01:39.580
That's what a classroom's all about.

00:01:40.950 --> 00:01:43.430
The swelling light of the laser

00:01:44.320 --> 00:01:49.880
told us eloquently, cruelly, that it was right on schedule.

00:01:51.190 --> 00:01:54.950
We had no time to hesitate.

00:01:52.210 --> 00:01:56.420
March 12th March 12th

00:01:57.320 --> 00:01:58.230
Everyone...

00:01:59.860 --> 00:02:02.120
We have to decide this ourselves.

00:02:08.440 --> 00:02:13.060
We could choose to stay out of this and leave it up to fate.

00:02:17.860 --> 00:02:22.660
Show of hands: Who doesn't want to kill Korosensei?

00:02:35.430 --> 00:02:37.480
Okay, hands down.

00:02:40.320 --> 00:02:41.700
Who wants to kill him?

00:02:58.930 --> 00:02:59.990
They were always with us:

00:03:00.680 --> 00:03:02.860
our guns, our knives...

00:03:03.410 --> 00:03:04.940
and our teacher.

00:03:14.130 --> 00:03:17.160
That was our answer.

00:03:19.220 --> 00:03:24.820
We were killers. Our target was our teacher.

00:03:29.560 --> 00:03:34.650
We were all painfully aware of what we had to do to our mentor

00:03:35.830 --> 00:03:39.160
for us to graduate with our bond still intact.

